170
00:13:56,880 --> 00:13:59,980
No. Vamos hoy.

171
00:14:00,480 --> 00:14:02,200
Sí.

172
00:14:04,990 --> 00:14:07,670
<i>- Adiós.<br>- Adiós.</i>

173
00:14:11,740 --> 00:14:13,910
- Seul Gi. <br>- Sí, gerente.

174
00:14:13,910 --> 00:14:16,600
